Insertion Sort Souffle.

This recipe sorts a list of integers using insertion sort.

Ingredients.
5 g unsorted numbers
3 g second number
1 g first number
4 g fourth number
2 g third number

Method.
Put first number into mixing bowl.
Put second number into mixing bowl.
Put third number into mixing bowl.
Put fourth number into mixing bowl.
Put unsorted numbers into mixing bowl.
Sort the mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
